Products.RichDescription:
MAGNUM ICE CONFECTION DAIRY FREE SEA SALT CARAMEL 270 ML
You can now experience Magnum Non-Dairy by taking an indulgent bite out of our new non-dairy Sea Salt Caramel bar velvety sea salt caramel flavoured indulgence dipped in sweet Belgian chocolate. The delicious and velvety plant-based ice cream bar has a balanced flavour and provides the indulgence of a classic Magnum, certified vegan by Vegan.org. This frozen dessert is plant-based and non-GMO. In addition to Magnum Non-Dairy Sea Salt Caramel, be sure to try Magnum Non-Dairy Classic and Magnum Non-Dairy Almond. At Magnum, we believe that a day without pleasure is a day lost. That's why we have been creating decadent ice cream indulgences since 1989. Explore the full range of Magnum ice cream bars and discover an expansive world of pleasure. Each flavour is made with Belgian chocolate that uses cocoa beans sourced from Rainforest Alliance Certified farms. Belgian chocolate has an outstanding reputation for its smooth, rich flavour and tempting chocolate aroma. It's recognised around the world because of its meticulous adherence to Old World craftsmanship. Magnum ice cream bars are crafted in this rich heritage and are made with a signature Belgian chocolate recipe developed specifically for us. While still warm, this delicious coating wraps around our velvety ice creams, instantly cooling to leave our signature solid, thick shell ready and waiting to be cracked. From intense to sweet to salty to dark, which one will be your next indulgence?

Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected by Rainforest Alliance Certified farmers. Magnum cocoa beans have a long way to go before they become Magnum chocolate. Were working closely with the Rainforest Alliance to make sure all our cocoa beans are responsibly sourced to produce our icecreams, sticks and tubs, in every flavour, with the best chocolate quality. Its about quality and sustainability throughout every step of the journey. Every Magnum stick, every Magnum tub represent the perfect, indulgent and delicious treat or snack for any family. Since 1989, Pleasure Seekers around the world have been discovering Magnum, and we have been taking pleasure very seriously. Thick Chocolate. Smooth ice cream. The perfect balance. To us, pleasure is everything. The pleasure of each individual and their freedom to experience it genuinely and in full. We know pleasure can be found in both the smallest and the biggest things. But only if you are brave enough will you really find your pleasure, your true pleasure that stays with you. We are Magnum, the champions of true pleasure.
Velvety sea salt caramel flavoured indulgence dipped in sweet Belgian chocolate
A true Magnum cracking experience, 100% Vegan and Dairy Free The perfect treat or snack in a stick for any family. A real Magnum Chocolate flavour in plant based ingredients.
This ice cream is plant-based, non-GMO, and certified vegan by Vegan.org
Magnum works closely with the Rainforest Alliance to make sure cocoa beans are sourced responsibly
Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is certified by Rainforest Alliance in any flavour. Magnum sticks are a delicious treat for every family.
Magnum chocolate dessert icecream is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected to deliver the best chocolate flavours to you.

Products.RichDescription:
SPLICE FRUIT ICE PINE LIME MP8 544 ML

Say goodbye serious and hello happiness! Streets Splice Pine Lime is a delicious fruit ice confection. Available in a multipack, so get your 8 pack today! Using real fruit juice this refreshing treat is perfect to cool down over Summer or anytime of the year. Splice is famous for its pineapple & lime flavoured coating with a soft vanilla centre, not to mention that it's 97% fat free! An Aussie classic that is ideal to share with friends and family, or to treat yourself! Get your hands on a delicious and refreshing Streets Splice Pine-Lime today. Between World War 1 and World War 2, Edwin (Ted) Street, thanks to his wife and brother, laid the foundations (in Corrimal, NSW) for what would ultimately become Australias biggest and best-known ice cream manufacturer. Streets ice cream was originally made in the back shed by Ted Street. He would then sell these to neighbours along with sweets, cakes and lemonade. Popularity grew, and he soon used a cart, then a one horse power motorbike to sell Streets ice cream. It continued to grow and today Streets ice cream is sold throughout Australia and New Zealand with well-known brands such as Magnum, Paddle Pop, Cornetto, Gaytime, Calippo and Blue Ribbon. Choose Happier Together.

Splice a refreshing fruit ice confection, so get the fruity feeling!

Splice delivers on a delicious Pine Lime flavour!

Splice contains no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Made with real fruit juice, great for the whole family.

97% fat free, makes a great refreshment treat.

Available in a multipack with 8 delicious sticks.

Products.RichDescription:
Steggles Crumbed Chicken Breast Fingers are delightfully crunchy. Ready in 15 minutes. Free from artificial colours or flavours. Our chickens have no added hormones and are a good source of protein.

Chicken Breast shaped and coated in a potato crumb.

We're Stegglers for quality time.

Quality time. It's never been more important to a family. It's time spent together.
It's about creating real family connections - the laughter, the stories and the conversations.
Which is why at Steggles we want to remind all Australian families just how special mealtime is around the table.
After all, we're not just Stegglers for quality.
We're Stegglers for quality time.

Free from artificial colours or flavours

Absolutely no added preservatives

Our Chickens have no added hormones
